data.description:
AMAZING 2 Story Floor plan Featuring 5 bedrooms, 4.5 Bathrooms, a Deep 3 car garage with built in storage, and fabulous backyard!! 
Huge open main level includes formal dining, great room, large hearth / living area, spacious granite kitchen, powder bath, see through fireplace, and drop zone entering from the garage! 
Upper level boosts 3 large secondary bedrooms, guest bathroom, jack n jill bathroom, walk in laundry, and the MASTER SUITE of your DREAMS!! 
Get ready to cheer on your favorite teams in the finished basement! The Basement has as incredible bar area, 5th bedroom, 4th full bathroom, and plenty of extra entertaining space! 
You will absolutely love the back covered lanai with fireplace, additional stamped patio, and large level fenced yard! 
Seller has made all the needed updates. All you have to do is MOVE IN and ENJOY!! 
Nestled in sought out Grey Oaks Subdivision with an awesome community pool and many walking trails. 
Great location putting you close to shopping, Hwy Access, and wonderful schools!
